Set up Angualr 2 envrionment source: https://www.barbarianmeetscoding.com
All commands are run in git bash on windows envrionment

1. install angular
npm install -g @angular/cli

2. create project (Only if you are starting a new project)
ng new angular-get-started --style scss

3. Install bootstrap for angular (cd to the porject directory first, i.e. front)
npm install ngx-bootstrap bootstrap --save

4. npm update

4. Test the project 
ng serve --open
